To use: create symbolic links to vim directory and vimrc in your home dir.

Contains:

rails.vim
NERD_tree
quickbuf
bclose (closes buffers without destroying window arrangement)
ir_black theme

Keys:

Arrows switch between splits (left right up down)
Ctrl-right and Ctrl-left switch between next and prev buffers
, is leader
Tab brings up quickbuf buffer list
Shift-Tab toggles nerd tree
